            <BuildableReference
               BuildableIdentifier = "primary"
               BlueprintIdentifier = "EF475AB12F56FC4600744F61"
               BuildableName = "minor protections. - No ad"
               BlueprintName = "You are a senior iOS engineer (SwiftUI) specialized in ActivityKit, Dynamic Island, and chat UX. Your task is to implement a Dynamic Island + Live Activities integration for AMEN that makes &#x201c;Smart Replies&#x201d; and &#x201c;Tone Assist&#x201d; interactive from the Dynamic Island for posts/comments/messages &#x2014; while staying Apple-native, subtle, and safe.  IMPORTANT CONSTRAINTS (NON-NEGOTIABLE) - Do NOT fake the Dynamic Island with a custom overlay. Use ActivityKit/Live Activities only. - Do NOT change AMEN&#x2019;s existing UI design language; only add the minimum needed for these features. - This must be fast and battery-safe: no constant updates, no polling loops, no heavy background work. - Privacy and safety must be respected:   - Do not show sensitive message content on lock screen unless user enables &#x201c;Show Previews&#x201d;.   - Do not generate or display unsafe text before moderation gating.   - Respect blocks/private accounts/minor protections. - No addictive mechanics: no &#x201c;trending&#x201d;, no engagement bait.  GOAL Enable a premium Dynamic Island experience that: 1) Shows a &#x201c;Reply&#x201d; Live Activity when a user receives a comment/mention/DM OR when the user long-presses a notification row. 2) Offers 2&#x2013;3 one-tap &#x201c;Smart Reply&#x201d; options generated by Berean AI (Encourage / Thoughtful Question / Prayer). 3) Provides &#x201c;Tone Assist&#x201d; if the user typed a reply in-app and it is flagged as harsh: surface a &#x201c;Rewrite gentler&#x201d; option in the Dynamic Island. 4) When user taps a smart reply option, it opens AMEN to the exact destination with the chosen reply pre-filled (or safely sent if you can do it without risky UX).  TOP 3 DYNAMIC ISLAND USE CASES TO IMPLEMENT A) Comment Reply Live Activity - Trigger: new comment on user&#x2019;s post, mention, or reply notification - Dynamic Island compact: commenter avatar (or app icon) + &#x201c;New comment&#x201d; - Expanded: show 3 smart reply chips: Encourage / Ask / Pray + a &#x201c;Open&#x201d; button - Tap chip behavior:    - Deep link to comment thread with composer prefilled with the selected reply text.    - Do NOT auto-send from the island (avoid accidental sends); require user to confirm/send in-app.  B) DM Reply Live Activity (Privacy First) - Trigger: new DM from a mutual or allowed sender - Compact: &#x201c;New message&#x201d; (no preview by default) - Expanded: 3 smart reply chips (short, neutral), plus &#x201c;Open chat&#x201d; - If user has enabled message previews, you may show a VERY short snippet. - Tap chip deep links to the thread with prefilled text.  C) Tone Assist Prompt - Trigger: user typed a reply in-app and taps &#x201c;Send&#x201d;, but moderation/tone check returns WARN with a suggested rewrite - Dynamic Island shows: &#x201c;Tone Assist&#x201d; (compact) - Expanded: &#x201c;Rewrite gentler&#x201d; chip + &#x201c;Edit&#x201d; button - Tap &#x201c;Rewrite gentler&#x201d; deep links back to the composer with suggested rewrite inserted.  AI / MODERATION RULES (CRITICAL) - All smart replies MUST be generated through Berean Orchestrator (multi-provider), but ONLY after:   1) retrieving minimal context (post topic + comment snippet if allowed)   2) running a safety + tone moderation gate on the generated suggestions - If moderation blocks suggestions, show fallback chips:   - &#x201c;I hear you.&#x201d; / &#x201c;Thanks for sharing.&#x201d; / &#x201c;I&#x2019;m praying for you.&#x201d; - Never display unsafe or private content on lock screen. - Add a user setting: Notifications &#x2192; &#x201c;Show Reply Suggestions&#x201d; and &#x201c;Show Previews&#x201d;.  ARCHITECTURE REQUIREMENTS 1) LiveActivityManager (single source of truth) - Prevent multiple concurrent &#x201c;reply&#x201d; live activities:   - Only one Reply Activity active at a time, with ability to update it to the newest event. - Add debouncing: if multiple comments arrive quickly, update the existing activity instead of creating new. - End the activity automatically after:   - user opens the destination   - user dismisses   - 15 minutes timeout  2) Deep Linking - Implement deep links:   - amen://comment?postId=...&amp;commentId=...&amp;prefill=...   - amen://chat?threadId=...&amp;prefill=... - Ensure routing works from cold start and background.  3) Data Contracts Define ActivityKit attributes: - ReplyActivityAttributes:   - type: enum {comment, dm, toneAssist}   - entityId (postId/threadId)   - subEntityId (commentId optional)   - displayName (actor name optional)   - avatarURL optional (or use cached image)   - suggestion1/2/3 (SHORT strings, &lt;=60 chars)   - privacyLevel enum {noPreview, previewAllowed}   - createdAt, expiresAt  4) Provider Routing for Suggestions - Use OpenAI for structured short suggestion generation (JSON with 3 strings). - Use Claude for nuanced tone if needed for &#x201c;gentler rewrite&#x201d;. - Use Vertex for safety classification / moderation gating (or whichever moderation layer exists in AMEN). - Implement fallbacks if any provider fails.  IMPLEMENTATION STEPS (DO IN ORDER) 1) Add iOS capabilities: Live Activities, ActivityKit, push to start/update Live Activities (if using remote updates). 2) Build ReplyActivityAttributes + Live Activity UI:    - minimal/compact/expanded regions    - show 3 chips + Open button    - keep visuals consistent and minimal 3) Build LiveActivityManager with:    - startReplyActivity(event)    - updateReplyActivity(event)    - endReplyActivity(reason)    - dedupe and timeout logic 4) Build suggestion generation pipeline:    - gather minimal context    - call BereanOrchestrator(task: SMART_REPLY or TONE_REWRITE)    - run moderation gate on suggestions    - return safe suggestions or fallbacks 5) Hook triggers:    - When in-app notification arrives for comment/DM/mention &#x2192; optionally start/update live activity    - When user long-presses a notification row &#x2192; start live activity with that entity    - When tone check warns on send &#x2192; start Tone Assist live activity 6) Add settings toggles:    - Show Reply Suggestions (on/off)    - Show Message Previews (on/off) 7) Verify behavior on devices without Dynamic Island:    - fallback to Lock Screen Live Activity display only  TEST CHECKLIST (MUST EXECUTE) - Comment arrives &#x2192; island appears &#x2192; expanded shows suggestions &#x2192; tap suggestion deep links to correct thread with prefill - DM arrives &#x2192; no preview unless enabled &#x2192; suggestions show &#x2192; tap works - Tone assist triggers on warn &#x2192; rewrite suggestion available &#x2192; tap returns to composer with rewrite - Ensure no sensitive content shown on lock screen by default - Ensure no duplicate live activities - Ensure battery safe: no frequent updates - Ensure no crashes when app is cold-started via deep link  DELIVERABLES - Swift code for:   - ReplyActivityAttributes   - Reply Live Activity UI (ActivityConfiguration)   - LiveActivityManager   - Deep link router updates   - Suggestion generation + moderation gating pipeline - Notes about any entitlements, Info.plist additions, and Xcode capabilities needed.  BEGIN NOW Implement this incrementally andActivityKit.FrameworkTests"
               ReferencedContainer = "container:AMENAPP.xcodeproj">
            </BuildableReference>
         </TestableReference>
